Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.78,0:00:37.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左慈）\N調子に乗り過ぎだよ 貴様ら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:42.21,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,Th... This is Zuoci?! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:42.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（壁(へき)）こ… これが 左慈か！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:46.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クッ… 何をしている…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.08,0:00:46.13,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,What am I doing? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:50.17,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,As our leader, now's the most important time... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.83,0:00:50.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今こそ\N隊を率いる私がヤツの前に出て
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.10,0:00:52.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,味方の士気を高めるとき
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.17,0:00:52.53,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,for me to step out in front of him to boost our morale! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.79,0:00:57.53,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,But... even knowing that... my body won't move. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.83,0:00:57.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 分かっていても 体が動かぬ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.73,0:01:01.18,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,It just won't! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:01.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,動かぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.30,0:01:05.54,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.51,0:01:10.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信(しん)）おいおい\Nお前(めえ)こそ 調子に乗り過ぎだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.26,0:01:10.50,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You're the one who's too cocky!
