Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:22.56,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Ancient China.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.13,0:01:27.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聖者の時代は終わりを告げ\N人間の欲望は解放されていた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.23,0:01:25.11,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,After learning that the era of saints had ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.11,0:01:27.71,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,human desire was unleashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.27,0:01:31.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦乱の嵐が\N500年にわたって吹き荒れ
