Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.18,0:01:34.21,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,until over one hundred states were reduced to merely seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:39.91,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,And now, a wind of great history gusts from the State of Qin in the far West.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.31,0:01:37.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして今 西の果ての国 秦(しん)から―
