Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:16.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:23.34,Kingdom-Title-Op,Title,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,0)}The Ultimate Blade
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:30.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:39.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（刺す音）\N（兵士）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:56.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政(せい)）トーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:05.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楊端和(ようたんわ)）さすが秦王\N自ら乱戦に向かっていくか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:03.64,Kingdom-Thought,Yang,0,0,0,,Just what I've come to expect, King of Qin. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:05.60,Kingdom-Thought,Yang,0,0,0,,You're delving into the melee on your own? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:08.34,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Have you felt that presence?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:09.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（戦士）気配がしませんか？\N（楊端和）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:15.21,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Is it Bajiou?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:17.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（戦士）バジオウですか？\N（楊端和）いや 恐らく あの少年だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:17.89,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,No... Most likely, it's that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:23.22,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,It looks like the crucial time has finally come over there as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:23.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,向こうも\Nいよいよ時が満ちたようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:36.32,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You're the one who's too cocky, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,調子に乗り過ぎだよ ボケ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:40.22,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:42.45,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:45.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“ああ？”じゃねえよ！ こらー！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:45.68,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Screw you, asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:54.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウッ… いってえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:54.81,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:58.62,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You're pretty quick, ya bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:58.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,速(はえ)えな この野郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:00.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぶっ殺す！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.01,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:07.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,トリャー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:36.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）な… 何だ？ あのガキは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:36.75,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Wh-What is that kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.95,0:05:42.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつも\N一刀でしとめる左慈さまと…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:42.48,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Zuoci is the man who always finished people in one stroke,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.74,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,but that boy's standing against him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:46.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,打ち合ってやがる！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:49.87,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Awesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:49.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂(てん)）すげえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.47,0:05:54.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信 頑張れ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:54.50,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Xin... Keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:55.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おら！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:02.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜだ… 信…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:02.36,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,How... Xin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:10.71,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,How is it that even though you're just a boy, you can fight against Zuoci?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:10.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（壁）なぜ 少年の君が\N左慈を相手に立ち向かえるんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:12.90,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,Aren't you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:13.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐ろしくないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:17.81,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,Where the hell you two hiding that kind of power?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:17.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君たちは 一体\Nどこに そんな力を秘めている？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:22.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッ… “君たち”？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:22.94,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,You {\i0}two{\i1}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:27.39,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,Lord Piao...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:27.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,漂(ひょう)どの…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:33.35,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,That's it. Lord Piao took the lead unflinchingly and cut through the Wang Qi army's forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:31.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ\N漂どのも あの王騎(おうき)軍を相手に―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:33.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひるむことなく先頭を切り進んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:35.53,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,What the hell are you two...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:35.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君たちは 一体…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:38.77,Kingdom-Flashback,Bi,0,0,0,,I'm going to be the greatest general under the heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:38.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）\N俺は天下の大将軍になるんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.82,0:06:42.59,Kingdom-Flashback,Bi,0,0,0,,The greatest general under the heavens?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:45.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（壁）“天下の大将軍”？\Nこれはまた途方もない夢だな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:45.05,Kingdom-Flashback,Bi,0,0,0,,That's and enormous dream, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:47.75,Kingdom-Flashback,Diao,0,0,0,,For someone so stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:50.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂）こいつ バカのわりに\N夢と態度だけは でっかいんだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:50.63,Kingdom-Flashback,Diao,0,0,0,,his dreams and his ego are huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.53,0:06:51.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つい この間まで―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:54.51,Kingdom-Flashback,Diao,0,0,0,,Just the other day he was racking his brain over if he could become a general...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:55.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうやったら将軍になれるのかも\N知らなかったド平民のくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:55.92,Kingdom-Flashback,Diao,0,0,0,,even though he's a bottom-rank commoner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:56.98,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,Sheddep!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:58.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）\Nうるせえ！ なるったら なるんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:58.44,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,I said I'll become it and I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:03.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに こいつは\N俺１人の夢じゃないからな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:00.27,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:03.26,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,this isn't just my dream alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:05.13,Kingdom-Flashback,Bi,0,0,0,,It's a perilous path!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:05.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）険しい道だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:10.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フン… 上等じゃねえか！\Nどんな道だろうと 俺は…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:08.65,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,I'm just fine with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:10.09,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,No matter what kinda path it is, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:11.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっとっと！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:16.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）だから 言っただろう\N“険しい道だ”と
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:16.07,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,It's like he said, a perilous path.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:19.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）て… てめえ… ふざけんな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:18.05,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,Y-You bastard,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:19.22,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,don't screw with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:23.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,将軍への道の険しさは\Nこんなものでは ないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:23.00,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Compared to the peril of the path to being a general, what we're doing today is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:27.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フン… 望むところだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:27.29,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,All right then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:32.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと ひとつ言っておくが\Nただの将軍じゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:32.69,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,But make sure you get it, I'm not gonna be {\i1}just{\i0} a general.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:36.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“天下の大将軍”だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:36.12,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,The greatest! General! Under! The Heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:37.22,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,Don't screw it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:38.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間違えるんじゃねえ！\N（政）そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:38.87,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:39.80,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:42.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）あっ… 政 てめえ\N今 バカにしただろう！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:40.81,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,Zheng, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:42.33,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,Were you just making fun of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:45.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそ！ 見てろ\N絶対 なってやるからな！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:45.32,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,Shit! Just watch me! I'm definitely gonna become it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:53.71,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,Can you... really become it... Xin? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:53.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（壁）\N本当になるというのか？ 信…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:00.28,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,If you can... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:00.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だとしたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドリャー！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:10.77,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,You, a nameless servant boy... becoming the greatest general under the heavens... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:10.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（壁）名もない下僕の身の君が\N天下の大将軍に…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:12.76,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,If that happens...! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:12.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だとしたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.16,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Fuck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:15.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）\Nよっしゃ 当たった！ ざまあみろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:15.87,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I hit ya! How's that, bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:17.30,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,This fight's only just beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:17.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっからが勝負だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:21.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）お… おい…\N（兵士）あ… ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:19.81,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:24.33,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! What're ya spacing out for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:25.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おらおら 何ボケッとしてんだよ\Nビビっちまったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:25.71,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Ya ain't scared, are ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:37.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… 何だ？ 今の\N全く見えなかった…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.14,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that...? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:37.53,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,I couldn't see it at all... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:39.41,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.17,0:08:46.69,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,Xin... If you really do become a great general... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.17,0:08:46.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（壁）信 君が\N本当に大将軍になるのだとしたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:51.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君は 中華統一を\N目指す大王の片腕となって―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:51.80,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,You'd be the right hand of the king who's aiming to unite all of China... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:53.43,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,and fly all over the world... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:53.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天下に羽ばたく！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:08:59.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だとしたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:08:59.81,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,Then... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:02.52,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,Then...! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:02.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だとしたら！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:06.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左慈）逝(い)け
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:06.19,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:15.03,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,I've already let one die. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:15.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（壁）私は既に１人 死なせている
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:19.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この少年は 絶対に殺させぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:19.15,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,But I'll never let this boy be killed! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:23.17,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,This one's shallow, too. But I cut him twice.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:23.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これも浅い …が ２度 斬った！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:26.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１歩 踏み込めば 取れる！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:26.89,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,If I can get one step further, I can kill him!  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:46.39,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}Biiiii!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:45.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,壁ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:51.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フゥ… 続きだ 小僧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:51.36,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,Let's continue, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:02.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（斬る音）\N（兵士）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:11.88,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Are you all right, my king?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:11.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）大王！ 大丈夫ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:13.19,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:16.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かまうな\Nこの程度 かすり傷にも入らぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:16.44,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,You couldn't even call this a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:19.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士１）\Nしかし 中に入り過ぎです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:19.31,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,But you're too deep into the fray!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:20.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大王は 我らのあとに…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:20.78,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,My king, you should get behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.43,Kingdom-Main,Weixing,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself... king.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:32.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏興(ぎこう)）大王 お覚悟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:34.15,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Weixing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:34.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魏興…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:55.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ… ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:04.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てめえ… よくも壁を…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:04.34,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Bastard... How could you do that to Bi...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:10.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なに？\N頭に食らった一撃のせいか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:10.45,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,What?! Is it because of the one attack I took to the head?! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:21.82,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,The sword is strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:21.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“剣は力”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:32.08,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,The sword is speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:31.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“剣は速さ”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:35.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:35.42,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:39.59,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,My strength is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:39.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,力が…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:42.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,共に最上を極める この俺は…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:42.84,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,To have reached the highest level with it, I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:46.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天下最強だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:46.89,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,the strongest under the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:54.40,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,{Eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:08.29,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,Hey, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:08.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左慈）おい 小僧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:11.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな左慈さまに傷をつけたな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:11.48,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,You harmed Lord Zuoci quite a bit, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:15.52,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,So how are you going to pay for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:16.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どう落とし前つけてくれるんだ？\Nお前　ああ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:21.40,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Like I thought... Lord Zuoci has completely snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:21.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり 左慈さま 完全にキレてるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:22.74,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:26.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり前だ　服を汚されただけで\N相手を真っ二つにするお方だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:26.22,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,This is the man who cuts a person in half just for dirtying his clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:30.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのガキ なぶり殺しにされるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:30.22,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,That kid... He's gonna be tortured to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:34.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…だな\Nそして これで勝負は決した
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:34.32,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yeah... And the bout is settled now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:37.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくぞ！\N（兵士）皆殺しだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:36.05,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:37.65,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We'll kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:58.70,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:12:58.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生きてる！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:04.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（斬る音）\N（兵士）グワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:10.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂）壁！ しっかりしろ 壁！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:10.76,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Bi! Get a hold of yourself! Bi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:14.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？ 何だ？ 何か言ったか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:13.03,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:14.04,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:17.93,Kingdom-Main,Bi,0,0,0,,How is... the battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:17.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（壁）戦況は？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:32.49,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Everyone's in tough fights...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:32.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな 苦戦してる…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:38.92,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Especially Xin...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:38.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,特に 信は…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:55.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦況は すごく不利だよ すごく…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:53.43,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,We're... at a really bad disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:55.38,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:03.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも 大丈夫だ！\Nだって こっちには信がいる！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:01.48,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,But it'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:03.82,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Because we have Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:12.19,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,No matter how beat up he gets, he never loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:11.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつは どんなに\Nボロボロになっても負けやしない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:14.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんなにボロボロになっても…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:14.44,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,No matter how bad it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:16.74,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,He'll definitely win!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:16.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対 勝つ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:19.96,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Xin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.38,0:14:19.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだろう？ 信！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:41.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）エイッ！ おら！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:44.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）グワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:49.80,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,Hey, hey. Who said it's okay to sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:49.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいおい\N誰が しゃがんでいいと言った？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:50.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,立たんか こら！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:51.29,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,Can't you stand, bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:59.96,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You guys formed a separate squadron to attack the inner palace, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:59.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした？ 貴様ら別動隊となって\N本殿を討つ算段だったのだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:02.38,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,Then give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:04.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ならば 行ってみよ！\Nこの俺を倒して！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:04.09,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,Defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:07.07,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,What's wrong, kid? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:09.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした？\N小僧 どうした！ 早く立たんか！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:09.09,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,Why don't you stand up already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:12.68,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,C'mon! C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.67,0:15:15.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう終わりか？ おらおらおら！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:13.97,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,Finished already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:16.24,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,C'mon! C'mon! C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:18.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,し… 信…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:18.94,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,X... Xin...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:20.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:25.32,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,4300)}Xiiiiin! {Fade out}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:28.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）来た！\N（左慈）おらー！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:26.91,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:51.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）ケッ… バカが！\N長々と しゃべりやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:49.06,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.06,0:15:51.08,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Blabbering on like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:58.36,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I didn't hear a damn word you said, so I'll need you to say it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:58.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全然 聞いてなかったから\Nもう一度 言ってくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:02.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰が天下最強だって？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:02.44,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Who the fuck's the strongest under the heavens?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:08.53,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Thanks to your idle chatter, I'm totally back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:08.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てめえの与太話のおかげで\Nすっかり元に戻っちまったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.72,0:16:11.02,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Now, stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:10.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ 立てよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:14.03,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I'll teach you who's the strongest under the heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:13.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰が天下最強か教えてやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:18.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏興）ほう… その若さで―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.69,0:16:18.43,Kingdom-Thought,Weixing,0,0,0,,Oh? Despite being so young, {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:21.79,Kingdom-Thought,Weixing,0,0,0,,he's able to stand before me, unflinchingly, while I'm mounted on my horse? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:21.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,騎馬した この魏興を前に\Nひるまぬとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:25.40,Kingdom-Thought,Weixing,0,0,0,,Even though he's in the royal family, he has the heart of a warrior! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:25.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王族ながら武心(ぶしん)が宿るか！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:28.30,Kingdom-Thought,Weixing,0,0,0,,Perhaps this is the second coming of King Zhao. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:28.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるいは 昭王(しょうおう)の再来か…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:29.41,Kingdom-Main,Weixing,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:32.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 生まれ落ちた時と場所が\N悪すぎたな！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:33.20,Kingdom-Main,Weixing,0,0,0,,The time and place you were born in were simply too unfortunate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:34.27,Kingdom-Main,Weixing,0,0,0,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:34.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,御免！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:41.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.06,Kingdom-Thought,Weixing,0,0,0,,What?! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:46.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君(しょうぶんくん)）馬上に\Nふんぞり返っとるわりには…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:46.98,Kingdom-Main,Changwenjun,0,0,0,,Having gotten so arrogant up on that horse,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:51.15,Kingdom-Main,Changwenjun,0,0,0,,your sword has gotten quite a bit lighter, Weixing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:50.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,随分と軽い剣だな 魏興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:52.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,昌文君！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:53.31,Kingdom-Main,Weixing,0,0,0,,Changwenjun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:58.40,Kingdom-Thought,Changwenjun,0,0,0,,Until the separate squadron has reached the inner palace... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:58.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別動隊が本殿にたどりつくまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:05.21,Kingdom-Thought,Changwenjun,0,0,0,,Until we strike down Chengjiao and Jie Shi...! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:05.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君）\N成蟜(せいきょう)と竭氏(けつし)を討ち取るまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:07.22,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,No matter what it takes, we must hold out here! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:07.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）\Nなんとしても ここは耐えしのぐ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:09.50,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Xin! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:09.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼んだぞ 信！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:15.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎）\N相変わらず渋いですね 昌文君は
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:15.66,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,That Changwenjun is glum as usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:20.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし １か所 見物できないことが\N残念ですねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.15,0:17:20.85,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,It's too bad I can't see what's going on in one area, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:22.85,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Are you there, Teng?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:25.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,騰(とう)は いますか？\N（騰）はっ！ お呼びでしょうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:25.23,Kingdom-Main,Teng,0,0,0,,Yes. You called?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:29.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あちらの回廊の様子を\N見てきてもらえますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:29.72,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Could you take a look at the state of things in the corridor over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.14,0:17:33.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい 誰か 右龍(うりゅう)へ…\N（王騎）あなたに言ってますよ 騰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:31.92,Kingdom-Main,Teng,0,0,0,,Hey, someone check the Youlong...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:33.83,Kingdom-Main-Alt,Wang,0,0,0,,I'm telling you to, Teng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし\Nあそこは左慈が守っているはず
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:36.83,Kingdom-Main,Teng,0,0,0,,But Zuoci should be guarding that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:39.24,Kingdom-Main,Teng,0,0,0,,The separate squadron is surely already wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:39.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,既に別動隊は全滅しているのでは？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.25,0:17:45.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎）あの回廊を抜けたら\N本殿までは阻むものはありません
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.83,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,If they make it through that corridor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:45.73,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,there will be nothing blocking them to get to the inner palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:50.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,肆氏(しし)は必勝を期して\N左慈を配置したのでしょうねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:50.61,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Jie Shi must have placed Zuoci there expecting certain victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:56.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし それを承知で 王と昌文君は\N別動隊を送ったのですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.15,0:17:56.76,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,But knowing that, the king and Changwenjun sent a separate force inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左慈を抜く自信があると？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.26,Kingdom-Main,Teng,0,0,0,,You're saying they're confident they can get past Zuoci?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.18,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:04.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ？ 自信があるかは さておき…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:04.25,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Setting aside whether they're confident or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:12.46,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,You can be sure that the two who hold the greatest amount of trust are fighting in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.94,0:18:08.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あそこでは\N２人が最も信頼を寄せている者が
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:13.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦っているということで\N間違いないでしょう フフフフッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:17.28,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:20.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか…\N遊んでいるうちに回復したか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:20.69,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,You recovered while I was playing around...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.49,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:27.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから どうした？\N結局は最初に戻っただけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:27.71,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,All we've done is go back to the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:31.46,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,You no longer have a mask to protect your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:31.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう頭を守る面は ないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.37,0:18:35.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次の一刀で\N少ない脳みそをぶちまけてやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:35.26,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,With my next strike, I'll smash a little bit of your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:43.87,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,That's right. One strike...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:43.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう 一刀だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.65,0:18:49.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チッ…\Nあちこち斬られて 血を流し過ぎた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.53,0:18:49.20,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,I've lost too much blood from being cut all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:53.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,感覚のねえとこが\Nちらほら ありやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:53.94,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,And I've got some places here and there where I can't feel anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.22,0:18:57.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,余力は一刀のみ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:57.44,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,I've only got strength for one slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:00.46,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,But that's plenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:02.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが それで十分だ\Nこれは木刀じゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:02.82,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,This isn't a wooden sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.71,0:19:07.83,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,This is... the king's sword I inherited from Piao!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:07.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは漂から受け継いだ王の剣だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:14.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ… ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.26,0:19:34.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見てろ 壁！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:35.25,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Watch me, Bi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:40.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うらぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:58.87,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,In both speed and strength, I have no equal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:58.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左慈）\N速さも力も 俺にかなう者なし
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:00.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:00.26,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.59,0:20:09.41,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Old man, it looks like so much blood rose to your head...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:09.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）\Nおっさん 頭に血が上り過ぎて―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:11.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気がつかなかったみたいだな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:11.42,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,that you didn't notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:18.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんた 壁に２回斬られて\N速さも力も半減してたって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:18.02,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,With the two cuts Bi gave you, your speed and strength were both reduced by half...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.59,0:20:22.40,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,That was for Bi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:22.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,壁への落とし前だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:26.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しっかり受け取れ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:26.99,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Take it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.03,0:20:47.46,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,I... was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:50.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左慈）この俺が こんなガキに…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:50.04,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,By... this brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:54.88,Kingdom-Main,Zuoci,0,0,0,,Bastard... What... are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:55.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様… 何者だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:20:58.49,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I'm Xin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.25,0:20:58.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:17.38,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I did it, Bi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:17.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やったぞ 壁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:33.48,Kingdom-Main,Bi,0,0,0,,You won... Why're you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:31.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（壁）勝利して…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.38,0:21:33.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッ…\N（壁）なぜ泣くのだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:40.98,Kingdom-Main,Bi,0,0,0,,Did someone close to you die or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:40.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰か親しい人でも死んだのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:47.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）壁！ 生きてたのか！\N（壁）フフフッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:45.64,Kingdom-Main,Bi,0,0,0,,Bi! You're alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:51.89,Kingdom-Main,Bi,0,0,0,,It looks like by drawing my hips back, the wound I took was a bit shallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:51.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腰が引けてた分 受けた傷も\Nちょっと浅かったようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:53.41,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You damn bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.93,0:21:55.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）てめえ この野郎！\Nびっくりさせやがって！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:55.17,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.17,0:22:00.03,Kingdom-Main,Bajiou,0,0,0,,The warrior Tajif says "That man is alive. It's all right."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.24,0:21:56.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（バジオウ）戦士 タジフは―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:59.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“その男は生きている\N大丈夫だ”と言っている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:02.22,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You're too late! Don't be telling that to me that now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:04.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）遅(おせ)えよ！ 今ごろ言うな！\N（笑い声）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:10.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうやら終わったようですねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.58,0:22:09.91,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,It seems it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.49,0:22:14.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王と昌文君が信頼を寄せる…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.50,0:22:13.74,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,The one the king and Changwenjun put their faith in...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.37,0:22:16.94,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,I wonder just what kind of person they are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.39,0:22:18.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一体 どんな者なのでしょうねえ？\Nフフフフッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:22.52,Kingdom-Main,Bi,0,0,0,,Everyone's really beat up...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:22.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（壁）皆 ボロボロだな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.52,0:22:25.68,Kingdom-Main,Bi,0,0,0,,But to be up against Zuoci and such numbers...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.53,0:22:27.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし あの大人数と左慈を相手に\N犠牲が２人とは―
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.68,0:22:30.03,Kingdom-Main,Bi,0,0,0,,and getting through with just two sacrifices, the Mountain People are beyond incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.20,0:22:30.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,山の民 恐るべしというところか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.54,0:22:34.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）まあ 大将さえ倒しちまえば\Nこんなもんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:34.16,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Well, if you can beat an enemy general, this is what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:37.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂）それより 壁\N寝てないで大丈夫なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.63,0:22:37.52,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Anyhow, Bi, are you gonna be all right with not resting?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.52,0:22:40.04,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,He can't sleep after we've come this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.55,0:22:39.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）\Nここまで来て 寝てられっかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.04,0:22:41.92,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Right, Brother Bi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.08,0:22:43.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なあ？ 壁のあんちゃん\N（壁）そのとおりだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.92,0:22:43.35,Kingdom-Main,Bi,0,0,0,,Exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:47.35,Kingdom-Main,Bi,0,0,0,,When we get down this corridor...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.32,0:22:49.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この回廊を抜ければ\N直ちに 本殿に着く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.35,0:22:49.36,Kingdom-Main,Bi,0,0,0,,we'll be right at the inner palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.79,0:22:52.43,Kingdom-Main,Bi,0,0,0,,And in there is the ringleader behind this all,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.86,0:22:53.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本殿には\Nこの一件の首謀者 成蟜がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:22:54.06,Kingdom-Main,Bi,0,0,0,,Chengjiao.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.39,0:22:57.93,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,Do you hear me, Xin?! {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:23:00.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（漂）いいな？ 信　託したぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.70,0:23:00.04,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,I'm entrusting this to you! {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.72,0:23:06.15,Kingdom-Main,Bi,0,0,0,,Are you ready, Xin?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.87,0:23:07.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（壁）覚悟はできてるか？ 信\N（信）おうよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.53,0:23:07.07,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.44,0:23:14.78,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,We'll defeat Chengjiao!
